  dialogueLines:
  - Hello!
  - I'm the tutorial NPC
  - You have double jump
  - You have gliding when holding Space
  - You have sprint when holding Left Shift
  - Track your stamina bar
  - 'Talk to all the NPC''s '
  - And watch carefully the numbers they say at the end
  - 'It could be an important 4 digits code for safe at the top of the hill '
  - Goodbye and have fun!
